Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:13.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my~ mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beneath your sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:33.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm burning alive in your light~
